NUMBER 1213
NAME Cozy Kitchen
REGION 0
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
CHANNEL 777
EXIT O 1211

ITEM 0 1007
;table
ITEM 1 215
;chair
ITEM 3 1123
;window
 

*DESCRIPTION_START
It's a cozy breakfast nook, complete with table and benches, smell of coffee 
and fresh baked muffins. 
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFENTRY
   IFVAR DAY = 0
      ECHO ALL Mrs. Olson bustles around the kitchen preparing dinner. As you enter, she gives you a quick smile and directs you to the dining room for dinner.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR DAY = 1
      ECHO ALL Mrs. Olson greets you with a bright smile, saying "If you'd like breakfast, just say so!"
    ENDIF
ENDIF
  
IFSAY Breakfast
       ECHO PLAYER With a cheery smile, Mrs. Olson tells you, "We have the following items available this morning. Just tell me what you want."
       ECHO PLAYER Orange juice, Coffee, Tea or milk
       ECHO PLAYER Pancakes, french toast or blueberry muffins
       ECHO PLAYER She adds, "Oh, please pick up your order as soon as I bring it so the table doesn't get too cluttered.
ENDIF

IFSAY Orange_juice
       ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson pours a glass of fresh squeezed orange juice and puts it on the table.
       NEWITEM 4 472
       NEWPUT 4 561 ADJ1=665 VAL2=5
      ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson brings %n a glass of fresh squeezed orange juice.
ENDIF
IFSAY Coffee
       ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson pours you a mug of steaming coffee and puts it on the table.
       NEWITEM 5 676
       NEWPUT 5 250 VAL2=5                                                    
       ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson brings %n a mug of steaming coffee.
ENDIF
IFSAY tea
       ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson pours steaming water over a tea bag and puts the cup on the table.
       ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson brings %n a cup of hot tea.
       NEWITEM 6 311
       NEWPUT 6 1020 VAL2=5                              
ENDIF

IFSAY milk
       ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson pours a glass of milk and puts it on the table.
       NEWITEM 4 472
       NEWPUT 4 654
       ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson bring %n a glass of milk.
ENDIF
IFSAY pancakes
        ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson flips three pancakes onto a plate and puts them in front of you.
        NEWPUT 0 1394
        ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson brings %n some  pancakes. 
ENDIF
IFSAY french_toast
        ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson brings you some french toast, smothered in syrup and butter.
        NEWPUT 0 1387 ADJ1=389
        ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson brings %n some french toast smothered in syrup and butter.
ENDIF
IFSAY  blueberry_muffin
        ECHO PLAYER Mrs. Olson brings you a blueberry muffin fresh out of the oven.
        NEWPUT 0 675 ADJ1=88
        ECHO OTHERS Mrs. Olson brings %n a fresh blueberry muffin.
ENDIF

