*DESCRIPTION_START
This bedroom is tastefully decorated in shades of green and brown. 
The picture window looks north along the coast. A small round table with 
two chairs is placed in front of the window, and on it is a bottle of 
champagne in an ice bucket. A chocolate mint is laid on the pillow. You 
notice that there is no phone, no television, nothing to mar the peace and 
restfulness you feel here.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
insert bed description here (velvet covers, satin sheets)
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
insert chair description here  
*DESCRIPTION_END

