*DESCRIPTION_START
You could almost believe that you are the only person in the world standing 
on this quiet outcropping of rock north of the jetty. Even the seagulls seem 
to favor the other side of the lighthouse. Off in the distance, whitecaps 
topping the waves presage winter's coming.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GO 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You start to dip your toe in the water, but realize it's lready far too cold for swimming.
ENDIF

