            ENDIF
            IFVAR DUMMY1 > 5
               ECHO PLAYER You feel oddly at peace, and a little more confident.
               ECHO OTHERS %n smiles, a serene look passing over %h face.
            ENDIF
            IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
               ECHO PLAYER You catch a flash of white from the corner of your eye and turn to look.      
               NEWITEM 9 1126
               EQUAL FLAG4 1
               PLREVENT 3
               CONTPLREVENT
               ECHO PLAYER You turn quickly and are startled to see a woman dressed in white standing by the rock.
            ENDIF   
        ENDIF               
     ENDIF           
 
IFPREVERB LOOK 9            
   IFVAR FLAG4 = 1
      ECHO PLAYER To your surprise, Lenore looks completely solid. She smiles at you and in a soft voice says...
      ECHO OTHERS %n starts in surprise and then listens intently, %i head cocked to one side.
      PLREVENT 3
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER "Thank you for remembering Tyler, %n. I'd like to reward you somehow..."
      PLREVENT 3
      CONTPLREVENT 
      ECHO PLAYER Suddenly, she smiles happily. 
      ECHO PLAYER "I know!" she exclaims. "If you search very carefully in the Blue Room, you'll find a treasure!"
      REMOVEITEM 9
   ENDIF
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER No matter how hard you try, you just can't see a thing.
ENDIF            

