ITEM 0 1386 ADJ1=1321

*DESCRIPTION_START
This small dock serves as a mooring place for The Three Sirens two pedal 
boats. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
              
VARIABLE PEDALBOAT


IFPREVERB GO 0
   CLEARVERB
   AFFECT 1209
   EQUAL PEDALBOAT PLRSINROOM
   AFFECT 1208
   IFVAR PEDALBOAT < 2
   ECHO PLAYER The dock attendant helps you into the seat and tells you to push the pedal when your ready to go.
   ECHO OTHERS The dock attendant helps %n into the seat
   DISBAND
   MOVE 1209
   POSITION SIT
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER The pedalboat is currently in use.           
ENDIF


NUMBER 1209
NAME The Pedalboat
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 777
REGION 0
ITEM 0 738                                    

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are sitting in a contoured plastic seat that seems to have been 
tailor made for your body. The pedals are precisely the in the right position 
for pushing. The bright canopy over your head flaps in the breeze with a 
bright snapping sound.
*DESCRIPTION_END

   

IFPREVERB PUSH 0
   IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
      ECHO PLAYER You push down on the pedals and the boat moves away from the dock.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      EQUAL FLAG1 1
      ECHO PLAYER The boat turns into the current heading toward the mainland.
      PLREVENT 3
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER You continue pedaling toward shore. The brisk north wind catches the awning, making it snap loudly.
      PLREVENT 3
      CONTPLREVENT 
      ECHO PLAYER You've pedaled more than halfway to the rocky beach now. With the current helping, you find it's quite easy.
      PLREVENT 3
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER You backpedal slightly, turning the nose of the boat so that it heads in toward the beach.
      PLREVENT 3
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER The bottom of the boat scrapes on the sand as you pedal it in to shore. You carefully stand and step out of your seat.
      MOVE 1203
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You continue pedaling the boat toward the mainland.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
       

                     

       


                      



